Interface IOrderArchive

      • getFillEntry

        ITagValues getFillEntry(String clOrdID,
                        int tag,
                        String value)
                 throws Exception
        Retrieves the fill for order with the given tag/value from archive. Note that this will return the original values of this fill, ignoring any later corrections or cancellations of this fill.

        If more than one exists, any one could be returned.

        Parameters:
        clOrdID - id used for retrieval.
        tag - Tag used for retrieval.
        value - Value of tag used for retrieval.
        Returns:
        null if no such fill.
        Throws:
        Exception - TBD
